34 9-27-334. Disposition — Dependent-neglected — Generally.
35 (a) If a juvenile is found to be dependent-neglected, the circuit
36 court may enter an order making any of the following dispositions:
99 03-19-2025 12:14:20 LJH010

As Engrossed: H3/19/25 SB320
1 (1) Order family services;
2 (2)(A) If it is in the best interest of the juvenile, transfer
