1 (A) Distribute a review report to all the parties or their
2 attorneys and the court-appointed special advocate, if appointed; or
3 (B) Upload into a shared case management database an
4 electronic copy of the court report.
5 (2)(A) The court report prepared by the department shall include
6 a summary of the compliance of the parties with the court orders and case
