As Engrossed: H3/19/25 SB320
1 (2)(A) The court may order that the father, mother, and child
2 submit to scientific testing for drug or alcohol abuse upon motion of any
3 party.
4 (B) A written report of the test results prepared by the
5 person conducting the test, or by a person under whose supervision or
6 direction the test and analysis have been performed, certified by an
