1 in a petition to terminate parental rights under § 9-35-325.
2 (e)(1) The petition shall set forth the following in plain and concise
3 words:
4 (A) The facts that, if proven, would bring the family or
5 juvenile within the court's jurisdiction;
6 (B) The section of this subchapter upon which jurisdiction
7 for the petition is based; and
