32 home opened as a provisional foster home may receive a monthly board payment
33 from the department for no more than six (6) months unless fully opened as a
34 foster home; and
35 (C) The department shall not be ordered to pay the
36 equivalent of board payments, adoption subsidies, or guardianship subsidies
