36 intake officer and the prosecuting attorney within twenty-four (24) hours so
328 03-19-2025 12:14:20 LJH010

As Engrossed: H3/19/25 SB320
1 that a petition may be filed under this subchapter; or
2 (C) Return the juvenile to his or her home.
